div.p: HIGH: CH Status Check (EVERY event) GET /company/12345678
LOW: Snov.io Domain Search POST webhook.snov.io/domain
LOW: Snov.io Email Finder POST webhook.snov.io/email
1. CH API Protection: HIGH priority for status checks 600 req/5min is primary constraint
2. Credit Management: Snov.io stops when credits exhausted Resume next month automatically
3. Dependency Gating: No officers without domain No emails without officers
4. Natural Load Reduction: Each gate filters ~40-60% Dramatically reduces downstream calls
